content:
Considerations for Date Columns:

Confirm that date values in a column are uniform in format and time zone. Inconsistences can occur within a data source and after merging data from multiple sources.

Perform the following tasks for date columns:

* Ensure consistent date formats using the Format Date transformation.
* Fix time zone differences in datetime columns by creating a calculated column with the Formula transformation to add or subtract hours to datetime values.
* Use unique labels for all date column labels in a dataset.
title: Ensuring Consistent Date Formats and Time Zones
